title: Hunt for missing MH370 flight ends in mystery
text:
Hunt for missing MH370 flight ends in mystery Tuesday, May 29, 2018 - 02:01
The underwater search for missing Malaysia Airlines flight MH370 has ended with no conclusive evidence of the airliner's fate, four years after it disappeared over the Indian Ocean in the world's biggest aviation mystery. Matthew Larotonda reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
